    "description": "In a world gone mad... one egg stands alone against the fowl horde! Can your dual-wielding ovum outlaw survive against an endless army of zombie chickens?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397630/extras/cda11360b62089c3dca28e7802b6bd3d.avif?t=1701889236\" width=616 height=206 /></span><br><br>From the makers of the hit web game Shell Shockers comes a single player arcade scramble like no other. Take control of your autofiring hard-boiled hero and battle the chicken villains. Can you survive til the rescue chopper arrives? <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397630/extras/fdb22aa084626b755b549cef5c2edaf3.poster.avif?t=1701889236\" width=590 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397630/extras/fdb22aa084626b755b549cef5c2edaf3.webm?t=1701889236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397630/extras/fdb22aa084626b755b549cef5c2edaf3.mp4?t=1701889236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Collect golden eggs and crowns to egg-cessorize everything! Unlock new weapons and egg-stra eggatar characters, each with its own unique skill tree! Journey to new chicken zones for even more poultry-pulverizing showdowns!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397630/extras/8b6e67f1733f10f903eb7dc577f324c3.avif?t=1701889236\" width=616 height=222 /></span><br><br>Madcap arcade mayhem from the guys who made Shell Shockers and Slayaway Camp and Plants vs Zombies, and some other games too. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397630/extras/b638d363ebcb97e64ca0a06cb09d70bc.poster.avif?t=1701889236\" width=590 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397630/extras/b638d363ebcb97e64ca0a06cb09d70bc.webm?t=1701889236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2397630/extras/b638d363ebcb97e64ca0a06cb09d70bc.mp4?t=1701889236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Confront enormous bosses as you struggle to unlock new apocalyptic zones! Unleash nuclear hell on vast swarms of pecking foes! Become the baddest egg of them all!",
